Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Ross Perot withraws
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yh7ll
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 24 Jul 1992
Ross Perot withdraws from the 1992 presidential race, the mystery surrounding his exit, and one tiny, fatal slip during Perot's speech to the NAACP.